description:
&lt;p&gt;Applications are invited for a Consultant Cardiologist with a special interest in Cardiac Electrophysiology at Queen Alexandra Hospital, Portsmouth.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The successful postholder will assist with the delivery of the arrhythmia, ablation and pacing services and will also take a share in the management of acute cardiac admissions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Candidates must hold a CCT in cardiology as well as being fully trained and independent in performing simple and complex ablation (AF) procedures.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details, or to arrange an informal visit, please contact Alex Hobson on 02392 286000 or via email – alex.hobson@porthosp.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Closing date: &lt;/strong&gt;Sunday 22nd November 2020&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Interview date: &lt;/strong&gt;Friday 11th December 2020&lt;/p&gt;
